projects:
[{'title': 'Strategic Review of a Company', 'date': {'start': {'month': 2, 'day': None, 'year': 2023}, 'end': {'month': 6, 'day': None, 'year': 2023}}, 'description': "During the project, we are placed in a situation as if we were the Management Team of a large multinational company, in our case that's Home Depot. In that role, our task is to conduct a Strategic Review of that multinational company and at the same time function as the Board of Directors (BoDs) for two other organisations. The MT needs to choose two business areas to focus on in the implementation of strategic goals and based on that to create a tactical plan. The tactical plan intends to determine the mid-term tactical level goals for the achievement of the strategic goals, clarify the planned course of action and identify needed changes in the relevant departments.", 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Vasil', 'last_name': 'Zhelyazkov', 'name': None, 'headline': 'International Business student'}]}, {'title': 'Drive your Business', 'date': {'start': {'month': 2, 'day': None, 'year': 2021}, 'end': {'month': 6, 'day': None, 'year': 2021}}, 'description': 'The Carlsberg Foundation has initiated a set-up of Vaccination Aid Organization (VAO) in the region of Toamasina, Madagascar. Carlsberg has ensured a three-year contract with the local healthcare services to provide supply kits for the authorized vaccines depending on the supply from the COVAX initiative. According to this contract, enough kits should be supplied to vaccinate 5.25 % of the population every year. In turn, the VAO will operate closely with the local healthcare services, the World Health Organization (WHO) and with the COVAX initiative to provide COVID-19 vaccination to the remote and hardly accessible areas of the country. The immediate goal of this subsidiary is to vaccinate, on average, 2.55 % of the population every year. The job of the management team is to deal with the finances, logistics, human resources management and marketing, and successfully complete the goals of the organization.', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Vasil', 'last_name': 'Zhelyazkov', 'name': None, 'headline': 'International Business student'}]}, {'title': 'Start-up Factory: Entrepreneurship', 'date': {'start': {'month': 9, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}, 'end': {'month': 6, 'day': None, 'year': 2021}}, 'description': 'Transforming an idea into a real product/service. 
About the app:
Quickway is the “Google maps” for the airports. The airport navigation feature is what makes us unique.​
You can even access the maps without needing an internet connection by downloading them beforehand. ​Moreover, it includes various features like the basic options to store all your travel info in one place, sync travel plans with your calendar or receive real-time flight alerts. ​And some advanced ones like faster security check, discounts in airport stores and the option to book a rent-a-car for your trip.​', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Vasil', 'last_name': 'Zhelyazkov', 'name': None, 'headline': 'International Business student'}]}, {'title': 'Develop your business', 'date': {'start': {'month': 9, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}, 'end': {'month': 12, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}}, 'description': 'Market development of the Swiss-based company Mein Küchenchef in Germany, provided with both internal and external analysis. ', 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Vasil', 'last_name': 'Zhelyazkov', 'name': None, 'headline': 'International Business student'}]}, {'title': 'Analyse your company', 'date': {'start': {'month': 2, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}, 'end': {'month': 6, 'day': None, 'year': 2020}}, 'description': "Both micro- and macroenvironmental analysis of the fictional company l'Essence, which operates in the cosmetics industry. Acting as a consultant team hired by the management board to find a solution for the problems within the HR, Supply chain and Finance departments, as well as the moral dilemma case.", 'contributors': [{'type': 'standardizedContributor', 'first_name': 'Vasil', 'last_name': 'Zhelyazkov', 'name': None, 'headline': 'International Business student'}]}, {'title': 'Investigate your market', 'date': {'start': {'month': 9, 'day': None, 'year': 2019}, 'end': {'month': 12, 'day': None, 'year': 2019}}, 'description': "Both External and internal analysis of the company Tesla and the market they operate in using the methods SWOT, Porter's 5 forces, PESTEL+D, Tripple bottom line and VRIO.
